DiamondPrice

Caixia Liu
2017-07-04

Introduction to DiamondPrice Application

  • This is a shiny application used to predict the price of a diamond.
  • Customers need to select the carat, cut, color, and clarity of the diamond they want.
  • The application will return the estimated price of the diamond.

Relation between diamond price and diamond characters

Data used to build the application

This application is built with data from 54,000 diamonds.
